overview: The Compleat Al is a mockumentary about the life of "Weird Al" Yankovic, from his birth to 1985. The title of the film is parody of the 80's documentary The Compleat Beatles. Although it is a mockumentary, it is roughly based on Yankovic's real life. The film also contains all of Yankovic's music videos up to 1985.
tagline: THE AMAZING AND ALMOST-TRUE LIFE STORY OF A ROCK AND ROLL LEGEND
title: The Compleat Al
